### JSON report — structured data
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analyze/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "iPhone 15"
}

### HTML report — open directly in browser
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analyze/html
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "Nike Air Max"
}

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
